# 🧠 Real-ESRGAN Image & Video Upscaler

> Enhance low-resolution images and videos using **Real-ESRGAN** — a powerful generative model for super-resolution.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🖼️ Image upscaling up to 4×
- 🎞️ Video frame-by-frame enhancement
- ⚙️ CPU & GPU support
- 🌐 Gradio-based modern UI

---

## 🛠️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Fetiiii/real-esrgan-upscaler.git
cd real-esrgan-upscaler
pip install -r requirements.txt
Then download the pretrained model (63 MB) from:
https://github.com/xinntao/Real-ESRGAN/releases/download/v0.1.0/RealESRGAN_x4plus.pth?utm_source=chatgpt.com
and place it in the project root.


▶️ Run Locally
python app.py
The Gradio UI will open automatically at http://127.0.0.1:7860.


🧠 Model Details
Backbone: RRDBNet (Residual-in-Residual Dense Blocks)
Scale: 4×
Training Dataset: DF2K + synthetic degradations
Framework: PyTorch

